# Per-project binary allowlist — extends the sandbox's default toolset.
# One binary NAME per line; it must already be installed on the host.
# Its Nix closure is bound read-only and it is added to PATH inside the sandbox.
# Blank lines and lines starting with '#' are ignored.
# Read once at launch — edits take effect on the next launch.
# Example:
#   git
#   jq
